CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 24, 1945, pg. 8, reads: "DELTAS WINE AND DINE NEW SOROS - Members of Delta Sigma Theta Sorority wined and dined fourteen new members of the sorority last Thursday evening at Stanley's Grill, following their initiation, which took place at the home of Soror Nancy Lee. The new sorors include Bethesda Westfield, Juanita Fletcher, Evelyn Meade, Toki Schalk, Virginia Douglass, Roberta Mann, Carolyn Howe, Gloria Ashton, Bernice and Mittie Vaughn, Lesora Wade, Jean Williams, Lorina Bowler and Miriam Harper. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Delta Sigma Theta Sorority members, including Bethesda Westfield, Juanita Fletcher, Evelyn Meade, Toki Schalk, Virginia Douglass, Roberta Mann, Carolyn Howe, Gloria Ashton, Bernice and Mittie Vaughn, Lesora Wade, Jean Williams, Lorina Bowler, and Miriam Harper, gathered around long table with some holding Delta Sigma Theta sign in background, in dining room Stanley's Tavern
